msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Installation"

#: ../../installation.rst:4 5cd0b47e6f0c4101890e916a0ef83895
msgid "This section covers the installation steps of the sofware."
msgstr "Cette section couvre les étapes d'installation du logiciel."

#: ../../installation.rst:7 0d218edca54e4c89847358af8faa1b13
msgid "System dependencies"
msgstr "Dépendances système"

#: ../../installation.rst:9 d4ee02e710af4d008ea1e664a0b678bb
msgid ""
"You need poetry 1.8.4 installed. ```bash curl -sSL https://install"
".python-poetry.org | python3 - --version 1.8.4 ``` Prerequisites "
"-------------"
msgstr ""
"Poetry 1.8.4 doit être installé. ```bash curl -sSL https://install"
".python-poetry.org | python3 - --version 1.8.4 ``` Prérequis "
"-------------"

#: ../../installation.rst:16 b73884081c3548be9166e461d3c64c9a
msgid ""
"You need to have Valkey cloned and installed in the same directory you "
"clone this template in: this repository and and `valkey` must be in the "
"same directory, and **not** `valkey` cloned in this directory."
msgstr ""
"Valkey doit être cloné et installé dans le même répertoire parent que "
"RansomLook : ce dépôt et `valkey` doivent être voisins, et **pas** "
"`valkey` cloné dans ce répertoire."

#: ../../installation.rst:21 0fd43eb0db474d42a10453974fb504b9
msgid "Valkey"
msgstr "Valkey"

#: ../../installation.rst:23 876b57e7a7d14f7c9490fd8864d0e011
msgid ""
"`Valkey <https://valkey.io/>`_: Valkey is an open source (BSD) high-"
"performance key/value datastore that supports a variety of workloads such"
" as caching, message queues, and can act as a primary database. Valkey "
"can run as either a standalone daemon or in a cluster, with options for "
"replication and high availability."
msgstr ""
"`Valkey <https://valkey.io/>`_ : Valkey est un datastore clé/valeur open-"
"source (BSD) haute performance qui supporte divers workloads (cache, "
"files de messages, base primaire). Il peut tourner en daemon autonome ou "
"en cluster, avec options de réplication et haute disponibilité."

#: ../../installation.rst:30 af4759b03ae141f8aa4ad22ac8dce923
msgid ""
"Valkey should be installed from the source, and the repository must be in"
" one directory up as the one you will be cloning RansomLook into."
msgstr ""
"Valkey doit être installé depuis les sources, et son dépôt doit être "
"situé un niveau au-dessus du répertoire où RansomLook sera cloné."

#: ../../installation.rst:33 c397a6626eae4da9a9a5bd480bc1dd3e
msgid "In order to compile and test valkey, you will need a few packages:"
msgstr "Pour compiler et tester Valkey, quelques paquets sont nécessaires :"

