msgid ""
"Run the following command to fetch the required javascript deps and run "
"RansomLook."
msgstr ""
"Lancer la commande suivante pour récupérer les dépendances JavaScript et "
"démarrer RansomLook."

#: ../../installation.rst:122 a93ea1dd70004f93bc28e95a3f874cbd
msgid ""
"With the default configuration, you can access the web interface on "
"`http://127.0.0.1:8000`."
